How do I redeem my credit card rewards?
Once you log in to your UMB online banking dashboard, you can access your credit card
rewards with the below steps:
Click your credit card account tile.
Near the top of the credit card account page, you’ll see two tabs.
Select the Details tab.
Scroll down to find your rewards point total. Scroll further to find a
link to access/redeem your credit card rewards.
Click the link under the Access/Redeem Rewards header.
